  • Object

          • edu.stanford.cs.pptx.code.PPVar<T>

  • public class PPVar<T>
extends PPVariable
    This class represents a typed variable in a stack frame. The type parameter is the value type.

    • Constructor Summary

      Returns a new variable object with the specified width and the default height.
